<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/cabinet-office> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We support the Prime Minister and ensure the effective running of government. We are also the corporate headquarters for government, in partnership with HM Treasury, and we take the lead in certain critical policy areas. The Cabinet Office is a ministerial department, supported by 29 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
